<!-- ================= ABSTRACT ================= -->
<section>
  <h2>Project Abstract</h2>

  <p>
    Maintaining a healthy diet is a major challenge for many individuals due to
    lack of nutritional awareness, busy lifestyles, and limited meal planning
    skills. Most existing meal applications rely on fixed recipes that may not
    match available ingredients or individual preferences.
  </p>

  <p>
    Balanced Plate addresses this problem by using AI to generate flexible meal
    suggestions based on user-provided ingredients, dietary preferences, and
    nutritional goals. The system emphasizes balance, sustainability, and
    personalization rather than rigid recipe selection.
  </p>
</section>

<!-- ================= PROBLEM STATEMENT ================= -->
<section>
  <h2>Problem Statement</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>Lack of awareness about balanced nutrition</li>
    <li>Difficulty in planning meals with available ingredients</li>
    <li>Overdependence on repetitive or unhealthy food choices</li>
    <li>Limited personalization in existing diet applications</li>
    <li>Complex interfaces that discourage regular use</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    These challenges indicate the need for a simple yet intelligent meal
    assistance system that adapts to user needs.
  </p>
</section>

<!-- ================= OBJECTIVES ================= -->
<section>
  <h2>Project Objectives</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>To promote healthy and balanced eating habits</li>
    <li>To provide ingredient-based meal recommendations</li>
    <li>To adapt meal suggestions based on user preferences</li>
    <li>To simplify nutrition planning using AI</li>
    <li>To create an intuitive and user-friendly interface</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<!-- ================= SYSTEM OVERVIEW ================= -->
<section>
  <h2>System Overview</h2>

  <p>
    Balanced Plate operates as an interactive AI assistant that communicates
    with users through a simple input interface. Users provide available
    ingredients, dietary preferences, and optional constraints.
  </p>

  <p>
    The AI engine analyzes the inputs, maps them to nutritional guidelines, and
    generates meal suggestions that maintain a balance of proteins,
    carbohydrates, fats, and essential nutrients.
  </p>
</section>

<!-- ================= KEY FEATURES ================= -->
<section>
  <h2>Key Features</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>Ingredient-based meal generation</li>
    <li>AI-powered nutrition reasoning</li>
    <li>Diet preference handling (vegetarian, non-vegetarian, etc.)</li>
    <li>Simple and guided user interaction</li>
    <li>Health-focused recommendation logic</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<!-- ================= TECHNOLOGIES USED ================= -->
<section>
  <h2>Technologies Used</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>Python for backend processing</li>
    <li>Artificial Intelligence and LLMs</li>
    <li>Prompt engineering for meal generation</li>
    <li>Streamlit for user interface</li>
    <li>API integration for AI models</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<!-- ================= WORKFLOW ================= -->
<section>
  <h2>System Workflow</h2>

  <ol>
    <li>User inputs available ingredients</li>
    <li>User specifies dietary preferences</li>
    <li>AI processes nutritional requirements</li>
    <li>Balanced meal suggestions are generated</li>
    <li>Output is presented in an easy-to-follow format</li>
  </ol>
</section>

<!-- ================= USE CASES ================= -->
<section>
  <h2>Use Case Scenarios</h2>

  <p>
    Balanced Plate is suitable for students, working professionals, families,
    and individuals seeking healthier meal planning without complexity.
  </p>

  <p>
    It is especially useful for people with limited cooking time or restricted
    ingredient availability.
  </p>
</section>

